  86:Middlewares/ST/STM32_WPAN/interface/patterns/ble_thread/tl/hci_tl.c ****    * Up to release version v1.2.0, a while loop was implemented to read out events from the queue a
  87:Middlewares/ST/STM32_WPAN/interface/patterns/ble_thread/tl/hci_tl.c ****    * it is not empty. However, in a bare metal implementation, this leads to calling in a "blocking
