  88:Middlewares/ST/STM32_WPAN/interface/patterns/ble_thread/tl/hci_tl.c ****    * hci_user_evt_proc() as long as events are received without giving the opportunity to run other
  89:Middlewares/ST/STM32_WPAN/interface/patterns/ble_thread/tl/hci_tl.c ****    * in the background.
  90:Middlewares/ST/STM32_WPAN/interface/patterns/ble_thread/tl/hci_tl.c ****    * From now, the events are reported one by one. When it is checked there is still an event pendi
  91:Middlewares/ST/STM32_WPAN/interface/patterns/ble_thread/tl/hci_tl.c ****    * a request to the user is made to call again hci_user_evt_proc().
